              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1842888216132554391">Betta is a 50 something woman who has just lost her husband and longs to get out of Boston where reminders of him surround her. So begins her renewing journey of discovery as she moves to a small town and goes about reinventing the second half of her life. <br/>A short sweet book by Elizabeth Berg whose insight I always enjoy. <br/>4 stars</span>

          </span>
        </div>


